@startuml
skin rose
title **GDP Message – UPDATE VALID Flow**

queue "**GDP Event Hub**" as Queue
participant "**GDP Message Consumer**" as Consumer
database "**Redis**\n**(Idempotency Key Store)**" as REDIS
participant "**SP Creditore**" as SPC
participant "**SP Debitore**" as SPD
database "**SRTP**" as SRTP

Queue -> Consumer: **GDP Message**
note left: **Status = VALID**

activate Consumer

Consumer -> REDIS: **Check Idempotency-Key**
activate REDIS

alt **Idempotency-Key already present**
  REDIS --> Consumer: **Key found**
  deactivate REDIS

  Consumer -> Consumer: **Discard duplicated message**
  note right
    **Message already processed**
    **or already in processing**
  end note

else **Idempotency-Key not present**
  REDIS --> Consumer: **Key not found**
  Consumer -> REDIS: **Save Idempotency-Key**
  REDIS --> Consumer: **Key saved**
  deactivate REDIS

  Consumer -> Consumer: **Check message operation**

  alt **Operation == UPDATE and Status == VALID**
    Consumer -> SPC: **Process UPDATE VALID operation**
    activate SPC

    SPC -> SPC: **Check RTP status is valid**
    note right
      **✅ Valid RTP statuses:**
      - **CREATED**
      - **SENT**
      - **ACCEPTED**
      - **USER_ACCEPTED**
    end note

    alt **RTP status is valid**
      SPC -> SRTP: **findRtpByOperationDispatcherKey**
      activate SRTP

      alt **RTP exists**
        SRTP --> SPC: **RTP**
        deactivate SRTP

        SPC -> SPD: **POST /sepa-request-to-pay-requests/{id}/cancellation-requests**
        note right: **Send cancellation request to SP Debitore**
        activate SPD

        alt **Async flow EPC**
          SPD --> SPC: **OK empty Body**
          SPC -> SPC: **Set RTP status to RFC_SENT**
          SPC -> SRTP: **Save RTP with RFC_SENT status**
          activate SRTP
          SRTP --> SPC: **Saved RTP**
          deactivate SRTP

        else **Sync flow EPC**
          SPD --> SPC: **OK payload**
          SPC -> SPC: **Set RTP status to CANCELLED**
          SPC -> SRTP: **Save RTP with CANCELLED status**
          activate SRTP
          SRTP --> SPC: **Saved RTP**
          deactivate SRTP

        else **Error Sync Response**
          SPD --> SPC: **Error response**
          SPC -> SPC: **Set RTP status to ERROR_CANCEL**
          SPC -> SRTP: **Save RTP with ERROR_CANCEL status**
          activate SRTP
          SRTP --> SPC: **Saved RTP**
          deactivate SRTP
        end

        deactivate SPD

        alt **RTP status is CANCELLED or CANCELLED with RFC**
          SPC -> SPD: **POST /sepa-request-to-pay**
          note right: **Send RTP to SP Debitore**
          activate SPD

          alt **SP Debitor accepts**
            SPD --> SPC: **Response**
            deactivate SPD

            SPC -> SPC: **Set RTP status to SENT**
            SPC -> SRTP: **Save RTP with SENT status**
            activate SRTP
            SRTP --> SPC: **Saved RTP**
            deactivate SRTP

          else **SP Debitor rejects**
            SPD --> SPC: **Error response**
            deactivate SPD
            note right: **Based on SP Debitore response**

            SPC -> SPC: **Set RTP status to REJECTED**
            SPC -> SRTP: **Save RTP with REJECTED status**
            activate SRTP
            SRTP --> SPC: **Saved RTP**
            deactivate SRTP
          end

        else **Cancellation not possible or already final state**
          SPC -> Consumer: **Skip to next operation**
        end

        SPC --> Consumer: **Updated RTP**

      else **RTP not found**
        SRTP --> SPC: **Not found**
        deactivate SRTP

        SPC -> SPC: **Create RTP in status CREATED**
        SPC -> SRTP: **Save RTP with CREATED status**
        activate SRTP
        SRTP --> SPC: **Saved RTP**
        deactivate SRTP

        SPC -> SPD: **POST /sepa-request-to-pay**
        note right: **Send RTP to SP Debitore**
        activate SPD

        alt **Debitor accepts**
          SPD --> SPC: **Response**
          deactivate SPD

          SPC -> SPC: **Set RTP status to SENT**
          SPC -> SRTP: **Save RTP with SENT status**
          activate SRTP
          SRTP --> SPC: **Saved RTP**
          deactivate SRTP

        else **Debitor rejects**
          SPD --> SPC: **Error response**
          deactivate SPD
          note right: **Based on SP Debitore response**

          SPC -> SPC: **Set RTP status to REJECTED**
          SPC -> SRTP: **Save RTP with REJECTED status**
          activate SRTP
          SRTP --> SPC: **Saved RTP**
          deactivate SRTP
        end
      end

    else **RTP status invalid**
      SPC --> Consumer: **Error – Invalid RTP status**
    end

    deactivate SPC

  else **Different Operation**
    Consumer -> Consumer: **Skip message**
    note right: **Operation is not UPDATE VALID**
  end
end

deactivate Consumer
@enduml